521
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:52,667
Dad wants us to go back
to mommy.

522
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:54,933
You're not going back to her.

523
00:25:55,067 --> 00:25:56,033
You can stay here.

524
00:25:56,167 --> 00:25:58,233
Hazel won't leave
you alone, Felma.

525
00:25:58,367 --> 00:25:59,133
She's serious.

526
00:25:59,267 --> 00:26:01,400
She will sue you, too.

527
00:26:01,533 --> 00:26:04,000
Manuel, why is that woman here?

528
00:26:04,133 --> 00:26:04,933
Where's Jessica?

529
00:26:05,067 --> 00:26:06,633
She'll be a part
of this negotiation.

530
00:26:06,767 --> 00:26:09,100
This is just between you and me.

531
00:26:09,267 --> 00:26:10,233
Who are these people?

532
00:26:10,367 --> 00:26:11,667
Attorney Butch Yeban.

533
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:14,533
I represent Miss Felma Ruiz
in all present

534
00:26:14,667 --> 00:26:15,967
and forthcoming legal matters.

535
00:26:16,100 --> 00:26:17,600
And I'm Attorney Aries Tulio,

536
00:26:17,733 --> 00:26:19,933
legal counsel
for Mr. Manuel Cruz.
